Version : 0.2_SNAPSHOT
Date : 2012-03-27
Author : Sylvain "Viish" Berfini
License : GPL v3
Repository = https://github.com/Viish/Iso2DJavaEngine

v0.1 Features (2012-03-25) :
* Draw Sprites in layouts
* Predefined layouts for map or characters
* Animate Sprites
* Move Sprites
* Rotate Sprites

v0.2_SNAPSHOT Features (2012-03-27) :
* Better Wrapper API
* More functions to the API
* Draws the map starting at 0,0 (bugfix)
* Be able to click on a Sprite and know which one has been clicked (started)
* Zoom/UnZoom the map (started)

v0.2 TODO List :
* Better Sprites' animations
* Be able to highligth a sprite using an Image mask
* Be able to rotate the map